               <msContents>
                  <summary>Zǝmmare Chants for the Whole Year, Zǝmmare, ዝማሬ፡. Incipit: ናሁ ጸሐፍነ አንቀጸ ዝማሬ ዘአራራይ ወዘዕዝል ወዘግዕዝ እምዮሐንስ አስከ ዮሐንስ, with musical notation, arranged for the feast days. F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-50r: Zǝmmare for the New Year and following. F<locus target="#50v">50v, </locus>-66v: Zǝmmare for the feast of the Assumption of Mary, Nahase 7, and following. F<locus target="#67r">67r</locus>-95r: Zǝmmare Mäwaś‘ǝt for the departed, መዋሥዕት። AṢZ 529–604.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
